Description




VGRASS Fashion Co. Ltd. is principally engaged in the design, manufacture and distribution of branded lady's apparels. Through the operation of proprietary shops, the Company mainly deals with fashion lady's apparels under the brand named VGRASS. The Company provides apparels, including dresses, pants, coats, shirts, skirts, cotton coats, down garments and windbreakers, among others; knitted products, including sweater series products, as well as accessories, including bags, jewelries and scarf , among others.


