Company Description                    




                        V-Grass Fashion Co. Ltd. engages in manufacturing apparels and other women's fashion wear. The company markets its products under the brand VGRASS. Incorporated in the year 2003, V-Grass Fashion Co. Ltd. is based in Nanjing.                    


